# HOST
###Create a Host
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json 

{
  "firstName": "Dominic",
  "lastName": "Maina",
  "hostEmail": "dommaina@example.com",
  "hostContact": "0712345678",
  "hostPasswordHash": "dompassword123"
}

