# BOOKINGS
### create booking
POST http://localhost:3000/booking
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingRoomNumber": "4A",
  "bookingGuestId": "8ad7d34d-a9e0-42c5-99dc-761b736c8e93",
  "checkinDate": "2026-07-16",
  "checkoutDate": "2026-07-18",
  "guestCount": 1,
  "totalAmount": "4500.00",
  "bookingStatus": "assigned"
}

### get all bookings
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/bookings

### get booking by its ID
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/bookings/bookingbyid/47c4155c-ed32-4cba-860a-05bc4752aeb8

### get booking guestID
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/bookings/bookingbyguestid/2c3e0176-f501-48e1-908c-c52f6f23465c

### get booking guestID
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/bookings/bookingbyguestid/8ad7d34d-a9e0-42c5-99dc-761b736c8e93

### update booking by 
PATCH http://localhost:3000/auth/bookings/updatebyid/47c4155c-ed32-4cba-860a-05bc4752aeb8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingGuestId": "8ad7d34d-a9e0-42c5-99dc-761b736c8e93",
  "bookingStatus": "assigned"
}

### delete a booking by its ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/auth/bookings/deletebyid/d566dc72-2208-4152-9c41-1760e4c6b273


